## Internationalization (i18n)

### Translation Guidelines

**DO:**

- Translate all content (headings, body, examples)
- Adapt cultural references (not just literal translation)
- Use locale-specific formats (dates, currency, phone numbers)
- Maintain same structure across all languages
- Keep component hierarchy identical

**DON'T:**

- Machine-translate without review
- Change component order between languages
- Omit sections in translations
- Use different example data that changes meaning

### Locale-Specific Content

